##  Project Summary

This repository contains the report *"Dictionary Learning via Sparse Bayesian Learning (DL-SBL) for Image Denoising"*.

- Implements DL-SBL for adaptive dictionary learning
- Uses Orthogonal Matching Pursuit (OMP) for reconstruction
- Achieves strong denoising performance (PSNR ~28–29 dB, SSIM ~0.80–0.85)
- Preserves structural details such as edges
- Future work: runtime optimization, color image extension, larger dataset.
